  "extract": "The Cameroon national football team, also known as the Indomitable Lions, represents Cameroon in men's international football. It is controlled by the Fédération Camerounaise de Football, a member of FIFA and its African confederation CAF.",
  "extract_html": "<p>The <b>Cameroon national football team</b>, also known as the <b>Indomitable Lions</b>, represents Cameroon in men's international football. It is controlled by the Fédération Camerounaise de Football, a member of FIFA and its African confederation CAF.</p>"
